<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>BRINGING IN THE SHEAVES!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zingkal kipatin zaidamna chi tuh in,
 Sun hun ale tuh in, nitak lam geiin;
 Buh min phat ding leh alak phat ding chu ngakin,
 Lawptakin chieh hitiu, I buhphal chawiin!

[V2]
 * I buhphal chawiin! I buhphal chawiin!
 Lawp takin chieh hitiu, I buhphal chawiin! (2)

[V3]
 2. Nisa nuoia tuh in, a lima le tuh in,
 Mei zing leh phalbi huihvawt khawksa loin;
 Dan leh lakkhawm phat leh, I sep I zawh tiengleh,
 Lawp takin chieh hitiu, I buhphal chawiin.

[V4]
 3. Kap kawma chiehin Lalpa di'n chipha tuh un,
 Lungkham, lungzinna hung tung zing mahlele;
 Lungkhamna a beih tieng aman ei lawp intin,
 Lawp takin chieh hitiu, I buhphal chawiin!</lyrics>
<hymn_number>284</hymn_number>
<author>Knowles Shaw, George Austin Minor</author>
</song>